latestIgtvVideos.title: It’s her birthday 🎂
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So finally your day came , but as usual you are not at all interested but still 😂 ! 
Umm what should i write for youu 💭. Yes you are Beautiful 🥰, but not like those girls in the magazines 🖐. She was beautiful, for the way she thought💭. She was beautiful, for the soarkle in her eyes when she talked about something she loved 💓. She was beautiful, fir her ability to make other people smile even if she was sad☹️. No , she wasn’t beautiful for something as temporary as her looks 😛. She was beautiful, deep down to her soul ❤️. She is the girl who don’t wake up with perfect hair🤓. Who don’t mind eating a Big Mac instead of salad🥗 . Who don’t wear 50 pounds of makeup💄. Who’d rather spend the day in sweatpants than skinny jeans 👖. Who actually loves the comfort of T-shirt 😍. Who don’t get all the guys 🤨. Who aren’t popular but feel like it, when they’re with friends🤪. Who stick to sneakers instead of heels👻. Who aren’t afraid to break a nail🙌🏻 . Who don’t always get their own way 🤟🏻. Who don’t get everything they want 💀. Who don’t need a guy to tell them that they are beautiful 😛❤️. The girl like @__the__night__owl__ 
And here is something special for you ❤️ . 
Apne gamm ki numaish na kar .
Apne nasibb ki khwaish na kar .
Jo tera he vo khud chl kar tere pas aaega . 
Tu use paane ki koshish na kar ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️. Once again a very happy birthday by heart 💓, Love you tons ❤️❤️!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Friendship ❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hola ! Yeah, i really have infinite things to write about us or i should say about you ! But you know if i start writing that , it’ll never stop however what i want to say is , you are the best thing happened in my life ever , like i just love when people use to chuck into us , like  who is she? ,  does she is your gf and all , so yeah I hereby let everyone know that , yes she is my everything , she is my mother , sister, gf (great friend) ,  even sometime my dad too 😂 jokes apart ! She is the purest soul and the kindest girl i have ever met , she always make me laugh with her weird things 😂😂 (ukwim) ! But yeah the special bond the magical bond I should say is like i also don’t believe that she is my senior mann😂😂🥂 , but sometimes she made me angry  with her weird  actions 🤪🤪 , and that too I can’t carry for long ! Sometimes i feel bad like if I’m unable to help you in some particular things , but i can assure that too you’ll handle very calmly ❤️ cheers to our unknown relationship , cheers to our bond 🥂🥂 ,  and i pray it will be remains forever and remarkable! 🥂❤️ And i must say , she is the strongest girl i have ever met !
